description: Returns the image tag details for a repository in a public registry.

parameters.name: repositoryName
parameters.description: The name of the repository that contains the image tag details to describe.

nested_items.name: imageTagDetails
nested_items.description: The image tag details for the images in the requested repository.

nested_items.name: imageTag
nested_items.description: The tag that's associated with the image.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The time stamp that indicates when the image tag was created.

nested_items.name: imageDetail
nested_items.description: An object that describes the details of an image.

nested_items.name: imageDigest
nested_items.description: The sha256 digest of the image manifest.

nested_items.name: imageSizeInBytes
nested_items.description: The size, in bytes, of the image in the repository.

nested_items.name: imagePushedAt
nested_items.description: The date and time, expressed in standard JavaScript date format, which the current image tag was pushed to the repository at.

nested_items.name: imageManifestMediaType
nested_items.description: The media type of the image manifest.

nested_items.name: artifactMediaType
nested_items.description: The artifact media type of the image.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The nextToken value to include in a future DescribeImageTags request. When the results of a DescribeImageTags request exceed maxResults, you can use this value to retrieve the next page of results. If there are no more results to return, this value is null.
